## Key Implementation Differences

| Aspect | Nostr | Telegram |
|--------|-------|----------|
| **Account Model** | Single account (DEFAULT_ACCOUNT_ID) | Multi-account via `accounts.<id>` |
| **Chat Types** | Direct only | Direct + Group |
| **Media** | No | Yes |
| **Connection** | WebSocket relays (persistent) | Bot API polling/webhook |
| **Auth** | Nostr keypair (NIP-04 encryption) | Bot token |
| **Group Support** | None (MVP) | Full groups with topics |
| **Threading** | Not applicable | Message reply chains |
| **Discovery** | Relay-based | Bot commands |
| **DM Policies** | pairing, allowlist, open, disabled | Same, plus group-level overrides |
| **Transport** | Persistent bus with reconnect | Polling with heartbeat / Webhook |

