Functions:
- `listPulseboardAccountIds(cfg): string[]` — returns `[DEFAULT_ACCOUNT_ID]` when token is present; empty otherwise
- `resolveDefaultPulseboardAccountId(cfg): string` — delegates to `resolveListedDefaultAccountId`
- `resolvePulseboardAccount({ cfg, accountId? }): ResolvedPulseboardAccount` — reads from `cfg.channels.pulseboard`; `configured` requires all three of token, serverUrl, username

